g interactions, focusing on clickable/hoverable highlights for standard queries like ROI calculations. I'm building a \"Resume Session\" button for loading mock or real states, alongside a \"Clear\" option.\n\nI'm thinking about mobile strategy, too, designing a responsive layout with Tailwind for a good experience across devices. I'm focusing on ensuring easy touch targets and a scrollable timeline, preventing squishing. Finally, I'm noting the files to modify (`/app/build/page.tsx`) and to leave untouched (landing page files and API endpoints), and I'm reviewing the list of launcher tools and routes to ensure accuracy.\n\n\n"}}
